ice swing", "7. Watches where the ball goes", "8. Repairs divots", "Bunkers & Penalty Areas (Passing knows 3 of 5)", "1. Enters bunkers on low side", "2. Plays without grounding club in bunker (may ground club in penalty areas)", "3. How to take relief from penalty area", "4. Rakes bunkers", "Putting Green (Passing knows 9 of 12)", "1. Lays clubs near the exit of each green on the way to the next tee", "2. How to repair ball mark on the putting green", "3. How to mark ball on putting green", "4. How to move marker out of way of a fellow competitor", "5. Avoids line of putt for fellow competitor or self", "6. One practice swing", "7. Order of play", "8. Attends flag stick while not standing on lines", "9. If flag stick is out, first to hole out puts it back in", "10. Exits putting green quickly to the next tee", "11. Correctly keeps score for self on the next tee", "12. Last hole played, remove hats, shake hands and thanks fellow competitors", "Scoring (Passing knows 4 of 4)", "1. Marker calls scores by three (4-4-5) to the player for whom they marked", "2. Players responsible for hole-by-hole score not total score", "3. Player signs score card", "4. Marker signs score card"], "bbox": [[0.117647, 0.092879, 0.5782319999999999, 0.012727], [0.117647, 0.12197, 0.234896, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.151061, 0.131509, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.165909, 0.39685700000000007, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.180455, 0.43568599999999996, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.195, 0.30104000000000003, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.209545, 0.260393, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.224091, 0.252419, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.238636, 0.15607900000000002, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.253182, 0.21661000000000002, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.267727, 0.23555700000000002, 0.012727], [0.117647, 0.297121, 0.278426, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.326212, 0.45778199999999997, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.340758, 0.385234, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.355303, 0.23347, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.369849, 0.21019699999999997, 0.012727], [0.147059, 0.384394, 0.176865, 